s analyze` CLI command exists yet.** Story references it in error messages but no such subcommand exists. Dev needs to create it or adjust messaging.\",\n   263→      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   264→      \"resolved\": false\n   265→    },\n   266→    {\n   267→      \"id\": \"migrated-8\",\n   268→      \"story\": \"2-2-observability-hook-enforcement\",\n   269→      \"description\": \"**sprint-status.yaml not updated by agent** — updated manually by harness-run.\",\n   270→      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   271→      \"resolved\": false\n   272→    },\n   273→    {\n   274→      \"id\": \"migrated-9\",\n   275→      \"story\": \"2-1-verification-observability-check\",\n   276→      \"description\": \"**Epic 0.5 appeared:** The create-story agent added a new Epic 0.5 (Stream-JSON Live Activity Display) to sprint-status.yaml despite being told not to modify it. This is a workflow compliance issue.\",\n   277→      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   278→      \"resolved\": false\n   279→    },\n   280→    {\n   281→      \"id\": \"migrated-10\",\n   282→      \"story\": \"2-1-verification-observability-check\",\n   283→      \"description\": \"**AC #1 integration risk:** Verifying that the verifier queries observability after docker exec requires a live verification session — hard to test in isolation.\",\n   284→      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   285→      \"resolved\": false\n   286→    },\n   287→    {\n   288→      \"id\": \"migrated-11\",\n   289→      \"story\": \"2-1-verification-observability-check\",\n   290→      \"description\": \"**Tag coupling risk:** `[OBSERVABILITY GAP]` tag format is a convention between prompt template and parser regex. If verifier (Claude) doesn't emit exact format, parser won't detect it.\",\n   291→      \"source\": \"retro\",\n   292→      \"resolved\": false\n   293→    },\n   294→    {\n   295→      \"id\": \"migrated-12\",\n   296→      \"story\": \"2-1-verification-observability-check\",\n   297→      \"description\": \"**Naming confusion